name: Trapped (itch) (Tabby Entertainment)
description:
Keep In mind
  • There are multiple endings

This Game Was Made For The 105th Game Jam

Limitation was everything must be unique. Which there are 13k note arrangements you can find. More you play the game the more you know what's going on. 

Controls

W/A/S/D For Movement

Q/E To Read Notes
